description: A California classic turned worldwide phenomenon, Jimboy's Tacos is just what you need when you're craving something great on the streets of Sacramento.The taste of Jimboy's has been satisfying taste buds young and old since 1954, so they've learned everything there is to know about good eating. Tacos, burritos, nachos, and more, this truck is serving it all. Sink your teeth into some of Sacramento's best, with the unforgettable Jimboy's Tacos.
name: Jimboy's Tacos
